OL,6,                              W/// Q",.!
OL,7,BThe rising popularity ofEalcopopsBhas  
OL,8,Bprompted the launch of a national      
OL,9,BtelephoneEhelplineBfor young people.   
OL,11,EDrinkline YouthBhas been set up by     
OL,12,Bthe charity Drinkline, and is aimed at 
OL,13,Bteenagers seeking confidential help and
OL,14,Badvice about either their own drinking 
OL,15,Bor that of their parents or friends.   
OL,17,EClub 140Bfound many young people drink 
OL,18,Balcopops, unaware of the danger they   
OL,19,Bare putting themselves in.             
