OL,7,BMany teenagers' first experiences with 
OL,8,Balcohol areEfar from sensible,Bsays    
OL,9,BDrinkline's director Sarah Berger.     
OL,11,B"It often involvesEbinge drinkingBand  
OL,12,Bany advice is ignored," she says.      
OL,14,B"Some teenagers get into difficulties  
OL,15,Bbecause theyEdon't know how strong the 
OL,16,Bdrink is.BToo much alcohol can lead to 
OL,17,Bthem making fools of themselves, having
OL,18,Baccidents, unprotected sex, or getting 
OL,19,Binto trouble with the law," she warns. 
