OL,7,BThere is aEcomplacencyBabout drinking  
OL,8,Balcohol which is dangerous, says       
OL,9,BDrinkline's director Sarah Berger.     
OL,11,B"People seemEmore worried about drugs,"
OL,12,Bshe says. But nowEalcopopsBhave brought
OL,13,Bunderage drinking back into focus.     
OL,15,B"There are so manyEnew drinksBwhich    
OL,16,Btaste like soft drinks that the        
OL,17,Bdivision between alcoholic and         
OL,18,Bnon-alcoholic isEblurred,"Bsays Sarah. 
