OL,7,BThe launch ofEDrinkline YouthBhas been 
OL,8,Bwelcomed by teenagers. Scott, 14, of   
OL,9,BHuddersfield toldEClub 140:            
OL,11,B"It's a great idea for people who have 
OL,12,Bproblems and need to talk to someone.  
OL,13,EAlcopopsBare part of the problem       
OL,14,Bbecause theyEtaste like fruit juiceBand
OL,15,Byou can get out of it really quickly.  
OL,17,B"Even my seven-year-old brother likes  
OL,18,Bthe taste of them. That's dangerous -  
OL,19,Bthey'reEstronger than you think."      
