OL,6,                              W/// Q",.!
OL,7,EAlcohol is a drug,Beven though it      
OL,8,Bdoesn't get as much media attention    
OL,9,Bas ecstasy, says 14-year-old Scott.    
OL,11,B"Alcohol may be legal butEit can become
OL,12,Ban addictive drug," he says.           
OL,14,BKirsty, 15, of Huddersfield, agrees.   
OL,15,B"We hear a lot about hard drugs and    
OL,16,Ealcohol's pushed aside,"Bshe says. "The
OL,17,Bsweet taste of alcopops makes it easier
OL,18,Bto drink more of them than you might of
OL,19,Bcans ofEcider or lager."               
