OL,7,BDrinking too much can lead to acute    
OL,8,Balcoholic poisoning - 1,000 under 15s  
OL,9,Bhave theirEstomachs pumpedBevery year. 
OL,11,B"Young people underestimate the        
OL,12,Estrength of alcohol in alcopops,Bwhich 
OL,13,Bare easy to get hold of too," says     
OL,14,BDrinkline's director Sarah Berger.     
OL,16,B"The aim ofEDrinkline YouthBis to help 
OL,17,Byoung people. Whether it's their own   
OL,18,Bdrinking or that of others that's the  
OL,19,Bproblem, they can call in confidence." 
